ed="T" n="0798a08"/><persName key="A010909">釋嚴峻</persName>，姓<name>樊</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000021026">濰州</placeName>人也。父任<placeName key="PL000000026833">硤州</placeName>長史、<name>昭<lb
ed="T" n="0798a09"/>王</name>府司馬。<persName key="A010909">峻</persName>性地夷然，學習明利。<date key="j19873221987686" from-iso="+0729-01-01" to-iso="+0729-12-31">年及十九</date>，<lb
ed="T" n="0798a10"/>應進士舉。倏罹荼蓼<ptr target="#n1130"/>，思報劬勞<ptr type="glossary" target="#g450"/>，投<placeName key="PL000000025497">南陽</placeName>佛<lb
ed="T" n="0798a11"/>寺。後抵<placeName key="PL000000027023"><placeName>荊州</placeName><placeName>玉泉山蘭若</placeName></placeName>，遇<persName key="A014098">真<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，示其<lb
ed="T" n="0798a12"/>禪觀，入城泊<placeName key="PL000000057611">大雲寺</placeName>。<persName key="A010909">峻</persName>秉持戒印，用之不<lb
ed="T" n="0798a13"/><anchor xml:id="beg0798sgsz1"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>祁</sic><corr>刓</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0798sgsz1"/><ptr type="glossary" target="#g451"/>；憑附浮囊<ptr type="glossary" target="#g387"/>，渡之攸<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g545"/>往。眾請臨壇，復舉<lb
ed="T" n="0798a14"/>律之宗主，僶俛<ptr type="glossary" target="#g452"/>承命。忽逢<persName key="A010911">觀淨<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，頓明<lb
ed="T" n="0798a15"/>心法。<date from-iso="+0766-12-22" key="j20011912001238" to-iso="+0767-02-07"><name>大曆</name>元年</date>，思往<placeName key="PL000000019385">清<choice resp="sgsz"><sic>涼</sic><corr>原</corr></choice>山</placeName><ptr target="#n1133"/>，未達<placeName key="PL000000019383">廬陵</placeName>，見<lb
ed="T" n="0798a16"/><persName key="A004865">顏魯公</persName><ptr target="#n1131"/>，一言相契，膠漆如也。<date from-iso="+0767-02-08" key="j20012392001326" to-iso="+0767-05-06">二年春</date>，<placeName key="PL000000019610">宜春</placeName>太<lb
ed="T" n="0798a17"/>守俾僧正馳疏請召。<date from-iso="+0769-02-15" key="j20019772002331" to-iso="+0770-02-04">四年</date>春，<placeName key="PL000000018628">洪州</placeName>刺史<persName key="A000519">李華</persName><ptr target="#n1132"/><lb
ed="T" n="0798a18"/>員外延入<placeName key="PL000000018600">大明寺</placeName>住止。<date from-iso="+0769-04-15" key="j20020362002065" to-iso="+0769-05-14">三月</date>中，俄命沐浴<lb
ed="T" n="0798a19"/>換衣，舉望空虛，合掌而逝，春秋五十九。遷<lb
ed="T" n="0798a20"/>塔，弟子<persName key="A010921">圓約</persName>等於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000018600">寺</ref>前大泉池立碑存焉。</p>
